metadata.name: La casa
metadata.description:
Dear, Home!
To me you have become an unfrequented place, but things weren't always this way, how you changed my life and made me feel alive.  Whenever I'm adrift in the depths of my own deceptions and desires, you helped me find myself again. How you sheltered me from the blazing summer suns and kept me warm from the dreadful winter colds. You bring ease not only to the body-some but also to the mind.
As I am yours in heart, and you are forever mine at last.

Admirer,
Egret.

High resolution file  2160 x 2160 pixels
